xt><ref type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb10815">Bahr, Hermann</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L01896">Schnitzler an Beer-Hofmann, 10. 12. 1909</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L01898">Schnitzler an Beer-Hofmann, Beer-Hofmann, [12. 12. 1909]</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L01891">Bahr an Schnitzler, 2. 12. 1909</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L01901">Schnitzler an Bahr, 14. 12. 1909</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
